        <item id="i6413c7bfddf5a2425e6513424af2270">
            <label key="7d5aee20aa92fc594d34cba322904ca8">
                <text>Solving a technological problem goes through several steps. The steps include:</text>
            </label>
            <label key="2ad58ffa28fd1d284f223eab1c864adc">
                <text>identifying the problem to be solved</text>
            </label>
            <label key="1fd9516e916cec54a22adc8b5353302d">
                <text>finding possible solutions to the problem</text>
            </label>
            <label key="5918b1e2b35af64fe30bf5ea482bb723">
                <text>choosing the best solution to the problem.</text>
            </label>
            <label key="3b2b782358cea99942a0ffed89201313">
                <text>Consider the following activities that could be involved in each step of improving the removal of metal filings from your factory floor.</text>
            </label>
            <label key="2902222693b679afd2d5cb6e5df6431c">
                <text>Match each of the five activities with the problem-solving step to which the activity belongs.</text>
            </label>
            <label key="6a2d71fd7409606e76e5c321c57029d9">
                <text>Match boxes by selecting one box in each column. You can remove a match by selecting the line and then selecting ‘x’.</text>
            </label>
            <label key="1e4599a0ec08d3e4ec8b858c60d1e63f">
                <text>
                    <strong>Activity</strong>
                </text>
            </label>
            <label key="28cc4119eef18e864150e30a495b00dc">
                <text>
                    <strong>Problem-solving step</strong>
                </text>
            </label>
            <label key="dd24c4f58a016cee61e635f178ae9037">
                <text>determining the amount and size of filings that must be removed from the factory floor</text>
            </label>
            <label key="57a444b7fc2f23a2f91be1105ba0a14b">
                <text>searching the internet for different equipment that might be used</text>
            </label>
            <label key="7d27586fea286f69f3dc07c8d4786eb8">
                <text>determining why the current magnetic cleaners do not fully remove all metal filings</text>
            </label>
            <label key="5ff8691a6d04bf6007e9e74d6327bb90">
                <text>choosing the best solution to the problem</text>
            </label>
            <label key="81923c34aaf393af79248a5ea44afd25">
                <text>comparing the performance of potentially suitable equipment</text>
            </label>
            <label key="807d731430a5e2fb68607c34c7f8ae50">
                <text>finding articles in industry journals on the different technologies used for removing iron filings</text>
            </label>
        </item>
